Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.32,0:00:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体 不听使唤…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 去感受法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和它融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 总士
