Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社团晨练？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她倒是说过今天不用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是又跑羽佐间家去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我能进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天那之后我被妈妈骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是要是害你迟到了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那点程度的 冲刺一下根本不是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意这种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你看起来比昨天精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要咲良 上学去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 羽佐间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还是来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 肯定很快就能来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这书很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是坐今早的船回来的吗 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才在CDC写报告 所以来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多事都辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学到不少东西了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子会有特别的色彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦 都说不是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我没看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城 你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 刚回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士 回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 难不成那就是绝美的最新一期！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等好久啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东京怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 你没见到艺人什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下课就跟近藤出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再到我家来玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的感觉是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是春日井甲洋
